<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/806914-hello-should-i-read-the-last">Hello, 
Should I read The Last Enchantment or the Once and Future King for my summer reading? I have not read any other books in the last enchantment series, but I am really into fantasy books that involve romance. If anyone has read both please let me know which one you found more enjoyable!
Thanks,
Ryan</a>
</div>
